Title: Jeg visste det var noe rart med henne
Actors: Josefine Frida Pettersen, Ulrikke Falch, Lisa Teige, Iman Meskini
Plot: It is Easter holiday, Noora and the rest of the girls go the cabin belonging to Chris' grandmother. On their way they meet a creepy boy. They also play with an Ouija board and Vilde believes Sana has supernatural abilities.
